ContentDesc_Zadnor-Hochebene: The IVth Legion has retreated to the barren plateaus of Zadnor, their imperial flagship looming ominously on the horizon. What they hope to gain from their newfound base of operations remains to be seen, but the Resistance refuses to stand idle. As both sides are pushed to their limit, who will emerge the victor as the battle for Bozja reaches its bloody climax?
FATEs_CE Eney Waves_Here Comes the Caval: The IVth Legion's reinforcements have arrived in the form of unmanned magitek horsemen. They must be stopped if the Resistance is to advance.
FATEs_CE Eney Waves_Lean, Mean, Magitek: Sicinius has a near-limitless supply of mechanical horrors to assail the Resistance, and it is clear he spared no effort in building this latest entourage of magitek weapons to bar their path.
FATEs_CE Eney Waves_On Serpents' Wings_D: A cadre of mages has summoned a knot of winged serpents to bar the Resistance's path. You must see their plans unraveled if you mean to overcome the IVth Legion.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_A Familiar Fa: Auracite taken from the High Seraph Ultima is said to grant its wielder their heart's desire...for a price. A price the IVth Legion Zealots paid gladly, confident this unspeakable horror will put an end to the Resistance.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_Feeling the B: Heavily inspired by the technological marvel of the helldivers, the imperials have launched their latest prototype, the blackburn, in a desperate attempt to extinguish the Resistance's hopes of victory.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_From Beyond t: For the IVth Legion Zealots, death is a small price to pay to bring ruin to their enemies. A price they paid quite willingly to summon forth the dread spirit Shemhazai.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_Looks to Die: Ayida's scales are said to be so resplendent, so beautiful, that a man could die of bliss from the mere sight of them. Her victims, were they still alive, would assure you it was her bone-crushing strength and venomous bite that did them in.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_Never Cry Wol: The mighty Hrodvitnir descends upon the battlefield, a beast of legend known to leave naught but icy ruin in its wake. Can the Resistance escape the grip of its gelid jaws?
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_There Would B: An imperial mage detachment has called down Hanbi, bringer of ruin, to expunge the Resistance from the plateaus of Zadnor. This otherworldly being demands a tribute of blood, and its thirst is insatiable.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_Time to Burn_: A creature of flame, thought to exist outside the boundaries of time, this 4th-make Belias is bound to the IVth Legion's mages, and it is compelled now to reduce the Resistance to ashes.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_With Diremite: The IVth Legion's beastmasters have a penchant for collecting the most fearsome creatures known to the realm. And now they have unleashed their prized catch from the Burn to turn back the Resistance.
FATEs_CE Notorious monster_Worn to a Sha: The IVth Legion has grown woefully desperate to unleash this beast upon the Resistance. It is said the alkonost casts no shadow until it has killed a man and claims theirs as its own. Thankfully for the alkonost, it now has plenty to choose from.
FATEs_CE Solo Fight_Head of the Snake_De: You at last stand face-to-face with Menenius sas Lanatus, commanding officer of the IVth Legion's forces in Bozja. Defeat him, and you may deal the heaviest of blows to the imperials' morale.
FATEs_CE Solo Fight_Taking the Lyon's Sh: Lyon has grown restless waiting in the wings, and would see the Resistance brought low by his own hands. Has anyone the strength to tame this feral beast once and for all?
FATEs_CE Solo Fight_The Broken Blade_Des: Dabog has been reforged into a foul new weapon, a creature malformed beyond recognition. This thinking, unfeeling biological weapon has but a singular purpose...
FATEs_Gather_Parts and Parcel_Desc: The IVth Legion has deployed a new type of magitek weapon. Seeking to obtain its components for intelligence purposes, the Resistance has launched an attack with the aid of its shinobi allies.
FATEs_Gather_Tanking Up_Desc: The IVth Legion's magitek unit has been discovered replenishing supplies in the field. Seeking to relieve them of their ceruleum, the Bozjan Resistance has launched a raid.
FATEs_Notorious monster_A Just Pursuit_D: It has been revealed that the criminals who fled Doma with one of its treasures in tow were none other than the onmyoji, and they have designs to hand it over to the imperials. They must answer for their crimes and the treasure returned to its rightful home.
FATEs_Notorious monster_A Relic Unleashe: The imperial army has the power of a relic at its disposal, and has not scrupled to deploy it in battle. Defeat Gilbrisbert the Puppetmaster and the 4th-make Famfrit to bring an end to their inexorable assault.
FATEs_Notorious monster_An End to Atroci: The fiendish mage Fabineau has been allowed to carry out his cruel, sadistic experiments for far too long. Join Llofii the Forthright to see that her former superior officer is served a fate befitting his heinous crimes.
FATEs_Notorious monster_An Immoral Dilem: Llofii's former superior officer, an unprincipled mage by the name of Fabineau, has been spotted on the fields of Zadnor. Considering his reputation for atrocities, it would be a mistake to let him operate freely in the region.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Another Pilot Ep: Enhanced beyond normal limits by experimental Garlean technology, both Dabog and his fearsome warmachina represent a threat that cannot be ignored. While Bajsaljen might prefer to capture the Bozjan pilot alive, Dabog's unrestrained hostility may not afford you that option.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Attack of the Su: Bajsaljen and his company have found themselves facing off against a squadron of advanced flying armor piloted by enhanced soldiers. If they are to prevail, they will need all the help they can get.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Challenge Accept: Ever imperious, the beastmaster Pagaga has returned to challenge Resistance soldiers to do battle with her fearsome pets. A lesson in humility is clearly in order.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Deadly Divinatio: Mysterious Far Easterners sworn to the IVth Imperial Legion have appeared on the front. The Resistance will require aid if they are to overcome these interlopers and their strange magicks.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Demented Mentor_: Meryall, a member of the new Gunnhildr's Blades, is confronted with a challenge no student should ever have to face─overcoming her tempered mentor. Aid the younger red mage in subduing the now-fanatical Lovro.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Hypertuned Havoc: The IVth Legion's magitek-powered soldier Dabog has returned to the battlefield, this time in a glorious golden magitek armor as beautiful as the circumstances surrounding its pilot are terrifying. Bring down Delta Gabriel Kai before it can rain destruction from the heavens.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Mean-spirited_De: Oboro and Tsubame have tracked down Yamatsumi─a notorious onmyoji who has joined forces with the imperial army. Assist the shinobi with apprehending this dangerous individual, lest they be overwhelmed by his shikigami minions.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Of Beasts and Br: The beastmaster Pagaga, whose puissance on the battlefield is surpassed only by her overweening pride, has been dispatched to the front lines. Take up arms alongside the Resistance, that you might cut her and her contingent of savage monstrosities down to size.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Seeq and You Wil: War Beasts captain Daguza has returned with yet another flock of red chocobos, but it appears he no longer has recruitment on his mind─only a good fight.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Sever the String: Gilbrisbert of the IVth Legion Zealots has obtained a sacred relic, twisting its powers to his demented will and sowing chaos across Zadnor. Bring an end to the puppetmaster's reign of terror here and now before it engulfs the whole realm.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Still Only Count: Clarricie, the beastmaster centurion, has returned with a new pet of truly mammoth proportions. Topple the prehistoric pachyderm before it tramples the Resistance into dust.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Supersoldier Ris: Resistance soldiers have tracked down their comrade Dabog, who has returned with an enhanced flying armor. If they are to have a chance of saving their comrade, they must first destroy the weapon.
FATEs_Notorious monster_Th'uban the Terr: An eldritch horror from a time long past has been set loose by the IVth Legion to do as it pleases on the battlefield. Show the monstrous Th'uban that he does not belong in this world.
FATEs_Notorious monster_The Beasts Are B: Never one to shy from the front lines, Pagaga and her fiendish menagerie once more rear their ugly heads before the Resistance forces. It falls to you to teach the blustery beastmaster a lesson in the virtue of knowing when to quit.
FATEs_Notorious monster_The Student Beca: Foiled in her first attempt, Meryall has a second chance to save her enthralled teacher. Weather the scarlet storm, and help capture the uncontrollable Lovro.
FATEs_Slay enemies_A Wrench in the Recon: A detachment of warmachina has descended on the area, seemingly for the purpose of gathering vital intelligence which the Garleans may employ against their Resistance foes. See that the imperials learn nothing─or at least do not return alive to report it.
A Wrench in the Reconnaissance Effort
FATEs_Slay enemies_Attack of the Machine: Sicinius has developed a new weapon, which he has produced in great numbers and sent to the battlefield. They are unmanned, so be free of guilt as you render every last one to scrap.
FATEs_Slay enemies_Breaking the Ice_Desc: The IVth Legion's mage detachment has unleashed a hulking ice golem. The creature must be eliminated before it can wreak untold havoc.
FATEs_Slay enemies_Meet the Puppetmaster: Wielding verboten arts that are fed by the lifeblood of sacrifices, a centurion by the name of Gilbrisbert has brought an army of living puppets to bear upon the realm. He must be driven back, lest more fall under his wicked spell.
FATEs_Slay enemies_When Mages Rage_Desc: A detachment of particularly puissant mages from the IVth Legion are wreaking havoc on the front lines with an array of destructive magicks. Take up arms alongside the Resistance and snuff them out before too much damage can be done.
npcyell_ids_11335_Text: Bah, you try my patience! Protect me, shikigami! I command it!
npcyell_ids_11338_Text: The greatest shikigami we have ever commanded... Fallen.
npcyell_ids_11340_Text: Your quiver of tricks is empty, Yamatsumi. Now surrender!
npcyell_ids_11467_Text: Owww, that hurts! Seriously, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>, you're a woman after my own heart!
npcyell_ids_11475_Text: Resistance scum. Finally, you show yourselves...
npcyell_ids_11476_Text: Come, my new and improved Dabog! Show these fools the power of Delta Gabriel Kai!
npcyell_ids_11477_Text: It is Dabog inside that golden machina? Gods have mercy...
npcyell_ids_11479_Text: This is hyperpilot Dabog. Target confirmed. Commencing combat operations...
npcyell_ids_11480_Text: This is hyperpilot Dabog. Hull damage...confirmed. Firepower...below acceptable parameters.
npcyell_ids_11481_Text: Deploying long-range assault nodes... Initiating omnidirectional attack...
npcyell_ids_11483_Text: This is hyperpilot Dabog. Hull integrity...compromised. Proceeding with combat operations...
npcyell_ids_11616_Text: On the Vochstein name...I swear I will not fall!
npcyell_ids_11617_Text: The “Beast King”? Hah! I'll show Lyon who truly deserves to wear the crown!
npcyell_ids_11618_Text: The Vochsteins are the true rulers of beastkind─now and forever!
npcyell_ids_11619_Text: Berda, Obda! I told you to stay put! Your wounds are not yet healed...
npcyell_ids_11623_Text: Berda, how sweet you are! Obda, let us fight as one to the end!
npcyell_ids_11625_Text: They're tougher than they look. No wonder Lyon felt he'd met his match...
npcyell_ids_11742_Text: Heh heh heh... You seem to be hard-pressed, my dear Yamatsumi.
npcyell_ids_11745_Text: But worry not, for your salvation has arrived. Speak your heart's most earnest wish to the relic I bear, and the path to it shall open.
npcyell_ids_11746_Text: Please, Dabog! Come back with us!
npcyell_ids_11747_Text: <bzzzt> Fools. The thing that stands before you is not Dabog.
npcyell_ids_11748_Text: I...I have only one wish: to see the onmyoji revived under the flag of a new nation!
npcyell_ids_11749_Text: Huh? There's a voice...a voice coming from the stone. I can... I─ Ungaaah! GWAAAH!!!
npcyell_ids_11750_Text: No, it is an organic component─one designed to extract the most out of our weaponry!
npcyell_ids_11751_Text: Hahaha! Haaahaha! Your wish is the relic's command!
npcyell_ids_11752_Text: You live now under my flag, puppets to obey my every command! You shall be revived, oh yes, and more majestically than you have ever dreamed!
npcyell_ids_11758_Text: Hahaha. A defeat, perhaps, but a fruitful one. I have seen the measure of the relic's strength, and I am not left wanting.
npcyell_ids_11759_Text: Wh-Who are these men!? Why do they all look like Dabog!?
npcyell_ids_11775_Text: Isn't it obvious? We have succeeded in mass-producing them. Go forth, my enhanced soldiers! Go forth and destroy the enemy!
npcyell_ids_11783_Text: But I know a lost cause when I see one, and you can make a man beg only so many times.
npcyell_ids_11786_Text: So, with that out of the way, let's get right to business... You're all chocobo fodder!
npcyell_ids_11789_Text: Gahahaha, there's nothing like a good rampage!
npcyell_ids_11790_Text: No hard feelings, eh? At the end of the day, I just need the coin to feed my own.
npcyell_ids_11793_Text: Godsdammit... Sorry, but I can't afford to die here. Someone needs to put meat and mead on the table, see?
npcyell_ids_11805_Text: Hah hah! You may think to find comfort in numbers, but they shall all be my puppets!
npcyell_ids_11817_Text: The enemy is fled! Well fought, brothers!
npcyell_ids_11864_Text: Mark you the weapon he wields? That man is Lovro─one of Gunnhildr's Blades!
npcyell_ids_11865_Text: You dare face me again, foul pretender to the red mantle!?
npcyell_ids_11866_Text: Aye, and this time, I will not fail.
npcyell_ids_11867_Text: I will honor you, my mentor...by subduing you in battle!
npcyell_ids_11868_Text: Foe to my queen. Prepare to meet your end!
npcyell_ids_11869_Text: Ugh! ...You truly are a master of the art! Yet I will prove myself the stronger!
npcyell_ids_11870_Text: I tire of this contest! If you seek my best, then you shall have it!
npcyell_ids_11871_Text: And I will weather the storm just as you taught me...with heart and steel!
npcyell_ids_11873_Text: My vital flame feeds the Crimson Scourge!
npcyell_ids_11875_Text: My aether... How feeble grows its fire...
npcyell_ids_11876_Text: Quickly, bind him while he is still weak!
npcyell_ids_11877_Text: <pant> <pant> <pant> It is done, Master Lovro. The healing can begin!
npcyell_ids_11900_Text: You appear to be Bozjan, sir, but how came you to this place?
npcyell_ids_11901_Text: ...Dabog? It is you, is it not? There were reports of your capture two years ago!
npcyell_ids_11902_Text: This is hyperpilot Dabog. Hostile forces confirmed. Initiating combat.
npcyell_ids_11904_Text: I recognize that warmachina! ...And now we know who the pilot was.
npcyell_ids_11905_Text: Dabog is not in his right mind, but he leaves us little choice. Defend yourselves!
npcyell_ids_11906_Text: Fight their control, Dabog! This is not who you are!
npcyell_ids_11907_Text: Energy levels dropping. Initiating subroutines. Launching alternative attack patterns.
npcyell_ids_11910_Text: This is hyperpilot Dabog. Hull integrity compromised. Retreating to base.
npcyell_ids_11911_Text: Dabog, wait! Let us help you!
npcyell_ids_11912_Text: Is tempering not abhorrent enough!? Must they seek out new ways to twist and control men's hearts!?
npcyell_ids_11914_Text: Then we must work doubly hard not to lose our own. We stay the course, and hope it also leads to his salvation...
npcyell_ids_11925_Text: So you are one of Gunnhildr's Blades, yes? Thank you for kindly volunteering this information.
npcyell_ids_11931_Text: Allow us to even the odds!
npcyell_ids_11938_Text: Thank you, my friends! Let us put an end to the Empire's villainy!
npcyell_ids_11971_Text: If none of them are Dabog, what have you done with him!?
npcyell_ids_11972_Text: Ah yes, subject VIII. He was a truly exceptional prototype.
npcyell_ids_11973_Text: Alas, his flesh eventually succumbed to the rigors of testing. Controlling such complex machinery takes a heavy toll, you see.
npcyell_ids_11974_Text: Fortunately, we were able to overcome this problem by means of the VIIth's data extraction technique.
npcyell_ids_11975_Text: From his combat expertise to his memories, we transferred everything into these enhanced soldiers.
npcyell_ids_11976_Text: What!? You heartless fiend! Does your depravity know no bounds!?
npcyell_ids_11977_Text: You will pay for this! We will avenge Dabog!
npcyell_ids_11978_Text: Impossible... That my enhanced unit should be wiped out...
npcyell_ids_11979_Text: So be it. I had intended to conduct more tests, but you leave me no choice. Savor your victory while you still can!
npcyell_ids_11982_Text: Indeed. We will fight, and we will triumph─for Dabog and everyone we have lost.
npcyell_ids_11983_Text: Come, my friends. Let us return to the encampment and prepare for the next battle.
npcyell_ids_12008_Text: You are...much changed. What have those fiends done to you!?
npcyell_ids_12035_Text: Hull integrity at 60%. Firepower insufficient. Requesting helldiver reinforcements.
npcyell_ids_12110_Text: Did I not hire you to provide enrichment for my newest acquisition?
npcyell_ids_12111_Text: He does so love to stomp, you see. There's nothing he enjoys more than the sound of shattering bone...
npcyell_ids_12113_Text: Save your grisly threats─our courage will not be so easily shaken. Form up! We take this oversized beast down!
npcyell_ids_12114_Text: You've had your fun, Lyuba! No more playing now!
npcyell_ids_12117_Text: Why...? Why am I here...down in the dirt?
npcyell_ids_12118_Text: I will see you all ground into meat slop!
npcyell_ids_12119_Text: Your minced remains will fill the feeding troughs of my menagerie!
npcyell_ids_12120_Text: Do not give chase! You only risk being ambushed. See to the wounded, and keep watch for approaching enemies.
npcyell_ids_12121_Text: I must say, this Clarricie is proving to be a problem. Where does she keep finding all these fantastic beasts?
npcyell_ids_12131_Text: He's calling in fire support, but this is no time to withdraw! We stand our ground!
npcyell_ids_12162_Text: Please, Dabog! Come to your senses! We are not your enemy!
npcyell_ids_12167_Text: This is hyperpilot Dabog. Energy levels below minimum. Combat capabilities severely compromised. Returning to base.
npcyell_ids_12170_Text: Yet again we have failed our friend, and he remains at the enemy's mercy...
npcyell_ids_12171_Text: There is nothing left to be done here. Let us return to the encampment.
npcyell_ids_12173_Text: No... Defeat is an insult to my queen! I will hold back nothing. NOTHING!
npcyell_ids_5_Text: There are too many of them!
npcyell_ids_62_Text: There are too many of them!
